com.chipsandwaycool.entity.team

类 Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chipsandwaycool.entity.team.Team
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Team
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    This object represents one of the sixty-four teams in the NCAA tournament. Each one is given a rank within its region, which is encapsulated here along with the team's name.
